            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">35.004</ph> Publicizing requirements and expanding research and development sources.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2240e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2254e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            In order to obtain a broad base of the best contractor sources from the scientific and industrial community, agencies must, in addition to following the requirements of <xref href="FAR-i1121120.dita#i1121120"
                        base="i1121120"
                        outputclass="fm:Part"
                        class="- topic/xref ">part  5</xref>, continually search for and develop information on sources (including small business concerns) competent to perform R&amp;D work. These efforts should include-</p>
					          <ol id="d2240e26" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2254e30" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Early identification and publication of agency R&amp;D needs and requirements, including publicizing through the Governmentwide point of entry (GPE) (see <xref href="FAR-i1121120.dita#i1121120"
                              base="i1121120"
                              outputclass="fm:Part"
                              class="- topic/xref ">part  5</xref>);</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2254e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Cooperation among technical personnel, contracting officers, and Government small business personnel early in the acquisition process; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2254e51" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Providing agency R&amp;D points of contact for potential sources.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2254e62" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            See <xref href="FAR-i1114845.dita#i1114845"
                        base="i1114845"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  9.7</xref> for information regarding R&amp;D pools and <xref href="FAR-i1114896.dita#i1114896"
                        base="i1114896"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  9.6</xref> for teaming arrangements.</p>
				        </li>
